sense1_gloss_de: den Boden aussaugen (die Nährstofe entfernen, wie es Pflanzen tun)
sense1_gloss_en: to suck the soil (remove the earth's nutrients - what plants do)
sense1_gloss_es: chupar el suelo (remover las sustancias nutritivas, como hacen las plantas)
sense1_gloss_it: succhiare il suolo; [rimuovere le sostanze nutritive come fanno le piante]
svezzare; [togliere il lattante dal seno materno]

sense1_gloss_de: gehen, um etwas für jemanden zu senden
sense1_gloss_en: to go to send something for someone
to carry something on one's shoulder
